                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "The masters of the d'ziriaks' light-weaving craft are occult practitioners, almost always <a aonid=\"11\" game-obj=\"Classes\">sorcerers</a> of the <a aonid=\"1\" game-obj=\"Bloodlines\">aberrant bloodline</a>. Light weavers prefer spells that provide light or create magical writing. In their hive cities, light weavers create art, lighting, signage, and magic wards. They also use their light weaving for entertainment and education."
            }
